        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 5. Dorsal views of head of Peristedion barbiger, posteriorly showing preopercular margin. A, HUMZ 189063, 185mm SL, acutely angled flange; B, HUMZ 168028, 153mm SL, right-angled flange; C, HUMZ 210625, 120mm SL, simple spine; D, HUMZ 189055, 184mm SL, bifurcate spine. Arrows point to preopercular margins. Scale bars:5mm." ;
